abstract: A large class of first-time lawmakers must grapple with the ways and wiles of the Capitol before shaking things up.
snippet: A large class of first-time lawmakers must grapple with the ways and wiles of the Capitol before shaking things up.
lead_paragraph: ALBANY — If the 2019 legislative session seemed to begin with a breath of fresh air, it may be because of the newcomers: The New York State Senate this week welcomed 17 new members, all but two of them Democrats.

headline_main: 5 Dance Performances to See in N.Y.C. This Weekend

abstract: As teams compete for spots in the conference championship games, Patrick Mahomes makes his playoff debut, Philip Rivers tries to beat the Patriots and Ezekiel Elliott looks to run all over the Rams.
snippet: As teams compete for spots in the conference championship games, Patrick Mahomes makes his playoff debut, Philip Rivers tries to beat the Patriots and Ezekiel Elliott looks to run all over the Rams.
lead_paragraph: It will be hard to match the excitement of the N.F.L.’s wild-card weekend, in which the Colts won with an upset on the road, the Cowboys barely survived against the Seahawks, the Chargers invented a new defense to stop the Ravens and the Eagles shocked the Bears with help from a tipped field-goal attempt.

headline_main: Donald Trump, Gavin Newsom, Clemson: Your Tuesday Briefing

abstract: The new legislative session kicked off on Wednesday, with Democrats in control of the Legislature and the governor’s office. But big fights still await.
snippet: The new legislative session kicked off on Wednesday, with Democrats in control of the Legislature and the governor’s office. But big fights still await.
lead_paragraph: ALBANY — The words “Albany” and “lively” are not often used together, but on Wednesday, the first day of the year’s legislative session, the halls of the New York State Capitol were roaring.
